## Title: |c3399FFGamePadHelper|r Inventory Covetous Countess
## APIVersion: 101049
## Version: 1.02
## Author: olegbl
## Description: |c3399FFGamePadHelper|r module that shows a magnifying glass icon next to treasures that are useful for the Covetous Countess quest. The icon is green if the item is useful for the currently active quest (if any) and white otherwise.
## DependsOn: GamePadHelper LibMultiIcon LibCovetousCountess

GamePadHelper_InventoryCovetousCountess.lua
